ns0:foreignObject.html:div: Look carefully at the picture of the water cycle. Answer the questions in a few words or a short sentence.

ns0:svg.ns0:text: Q1. What is happening in this picture?
Q2. How many clouds do you see in the picture?
Q3. What is the water doing as it falls from the clouds?
Q4. Have you seen rain or water falling from clouds before? Where were you?
Q5. What do you think will happen to the water that has fallen on the ground?
